track_notes: This track represents the western portion of the activation zone that is not on Tribal Land. Different maps depict the USFS/Tribal boundary slightly different.   This track/shape uses the most conservative boundary lines
track_title: Portion of AZ on USFS Land

track_notes: Route starts at the junction of the Pacific Crest Trail (PCT) and the Lost Valley Road.  This is also the trailhead for Combs Peak and South Combs Peak.  The PCT passes with 1/4th mile of the summit.  Last 1/4 mile of track is a bushwhack to the summit.
